name: Louis Barber
description: I am very romantic and I like to pay a lot of attention to my man. I also like to give him compliments and tell her how nice looking he is and how much I love him.. It is usual for me to do nice things and buy presents for my man. I am a very good communicator and I love to talk things over. I hate to argue, and I am a very honest and caring woman. I would like for my future man to be able to work along with me…
